18#ifndef _LVM_REPORT_H
19#define _LVM_REPORT_H
20
21#include "metadata-exported.h"
22
23typedef enum {
24 LVS = 1,
25 PVS = 2,
26 VGS = 4,
27 SEGS = 8,
28 PVSEGS = 16,
29 LABEL = 32
30} report_type_t;
31
32struct field;
33struct report_handle;
34
35typedef int (*field_report_fn) (struct report_handle * dh, struct field * field,
36 const void *data);
37
38void *report_init(struct cmd_context *cmd, const char *format, const char *keys,
39 report_type_t *report_type, const char *separator,
40 int aligned, int buffered, int headings, int field_prefixes,
41 int quoted, int columns_as_rows);
42void report_free(void *handle);
43int report_object(void *handle, struct volume_group *vg,
44 struct logical_volume *lv, struct physical_volume *pv,
45 struct lv_segment *seg, struct pv_segment *pvseg);
46int report_output(void *handle);
47
48#endif
